# Work DAG -- COMPUTER-USE Domain

> Generated: 2026-06-23. Source of truth: `phenotype-org-audits` audit pillars L0-L71.
> Scope: 9 repos across Eidolon (new), Dino (absorb), kmobile, kvirtstage, kvirtdesktop, mobile-mpc, mobilecli, playcua_ci_test, phenotype-journeys + 2 process repos (agileplus, phenotype-registry).
> Horizon: 6-12 months. Render cadence: weekly. Re-emit after each PR close.

---

