### T3. Critical path (12-week MVP to Eidolon v0.1)

```
A001 -> A005 -> A007 -> B001 -> C001 -> C010 -> C020 -> C040 -> C070 -> E001 -> E010 -> E020 -> E040
 ^     ^       ^       ^       ^       ^        ^        ^        ^        ^       ^        ^        ^
absorb Eidolon Eidolon Eidolon Eidolon Eidolon  Eidolon  Eidolon  Eidolon  Eidolon cua    cua    release
fork   scaffold IDL     bus     MCP     tools    bench    skill    SDK      MCP    port    publish
```

Wall-clock estimate: 12 weeks with 3 parallel agent workers + 1 human review node per PR.

### T4. Risk register

| ID | Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|----|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| R1 | Absorb bundle loses commits | M | H | 3-stage verify (grafts, fast-export diff, CI parity test) |
| R2 | Eidolon-MCP wire format drifts from mobile-mpc | H | M | Single codegen source under xtask + versioned schema |
| R3 | Playwright-MCP embed breaks on Playwright minor bump | M | M | Pin version, upstream weekly bump bot |
| R4 | cua-bench portability on macOS sandbox | M | M | Use Lume VM, not bare-metal; document host reqs |
| R5 | kvm/libvirt not available on macOS runners | H | L | Detect host; fallback to Docker on macOS, KVM on Linux |
| R6 | VNC/RDP/wayland bridge inconsistency | M | M | Per-display abstraction trait; one impl per display per OS |
| R7 | mobile-mpc agent-browser WebSocket lifecycle | M | M | Reconnect w/ exponential backoff, surface state via MCP |
| R8 | OTel cardinality explosion in agent loops | M | M | Bounded attribute set, 100k span cap per session |
| R9 | release-plz credential leak via workflow | L | H | Use OIDC + GitHub App, scoped secrets only |
| R10 | fuzz harness seeds PII | L | H | Corpus generation under `corpus-gen/` with PR review |

