---

## Execution Schedule (6-12 months)

| Quarter | Focus | Key WPs |
|---------|-------|---------|
| Q3 2026 (Jul-Sep) | Foundation + Eidolon scaffold | Blocks A, B, C, D |
| Q4 2026 (Oct-Dec) | Core extensions + SOTA ports | Blocks E, F, G, H, I |
| Q1 2027 (Jan-Mar) | Hygiene + Stabilize | Blocks J, K, L, M |
| Q2 2027 (Apr-Jun) | Polish + Observability | Blocks N, O, P, Q, R |
| Q3 2027 (Jul-Sep) | Optimize + DX | Blocks S, T, U |

This DAG is the canonical 6-12 month plan for the computer-use domain. It is intended to be re-rendered weekly as auditors surface new findings.
